tagline: We Prove It Before You Buy
targetAudience: 50-65+ technology-hesitant business owners who've been burned by agencies
conceptDescription: The Proof Seal represents verification - like a notary's embossed seal or engineer's stamp. Three concentric elements with gold proof points at center, conveying authority and verified expertise.

logos.name: seal-1
logos.description: Conservative interpretation - clean concentric rings with proof points
logos.designNotes: Classic notary-style seal with scalloped navy outer edge, multiple concentric rings in navy and gold, radiating tick marks suggesting precision measurement, and centered 'SV' monogram. The scalloped edge gives it the authentic feel of a wax seal impression.

logos.name: seal-2
logos.description: Push creativity - more distinctive seal/emblem execution
logos.designNotes: Sophisticated compass-like verification mark with four gold proof points at cardinal positions, concentric navy rings with intentional breaks suggesting calibration marks, radiating lines around center 'V' checkmark symbol, and elegant gold outer accent ring. Feels like a precision instrument or astronomical chart.

logos.name: seal-3
logos.description: Maximum creativity - extraordinary verification mark while staying professional
logos.designNotes: Bold reimagined seal with navy scalloped badge shape, golden spiral forming inward to center (suggesting the fingerprint of authenticity), and arrow emerging from spiral pointing upward-right (suggesting proven growth/results). The spiral evokes both a wax seal impression and the journey of verification leading to breakthrough results.
